Name: Alex
Video_Title: Exploring the secret world of vaporizer tricks and mods
Description: last week, the e-cigarette industry had a run-in with the girl scouts. the issue? thin mint-flavored e-liquid. wacky flavors are a huge part of the culture that has cropped up around nicotine vaporizers, but it doesn't stop there. in addition to creating their own custom flavors, vapers like to tamper with the insides of their devices to make what are called "mods." it's sort of like rolling your own cigarettes rather than buying packs. vape shops do a robust business in "rebuildable" devices, while the internet offers endless youtube videos and forum posts explaining how to alter the atomizer to get a stronger flavor or tweak the battery to get a deeper puff. just be careful it doesn't explode.

Video_Title: VooPoo Vinci 40W Mod Pod - Unboxing & Review
Description:
the vinci by voopoo is available from 180 smoke stores across canada, and at https://www.180smoke.ca/voopoo-vinci-40w-pod-mod

for more gear, e-liquid, and vaporizers, visit us at http://www.180smoke.com or http://www.180smoke.ca

be sure to stay connected with us through our social media!  we'll keep you updated on all the new products we get and deals we offer.
https://www.instagram.com/180smoke
https://twitter.com/180smoke
https://www.facebook.com/180smoke

the voopoo vinci is a compact 40w mod pod system with stylish and ergonomic design, and a versatile gene.ai chipset powered by a 1500mah internal cell that delivers a superior vaping experience. the rectangular aluminum alloy chassis is lightweight and durable with comfortable to grip beveled edges, and the side inlay panels are strikingly colorful. the magnetic pod attaches firmly to the base and has a side fill port with large silicone plug, capacity for 5.5ml e-liquid, and a wide built in mouthpiece. the pod is compatible with the pnp series of dl, half-dl, and ml press fit coils, and the draw is determined by the direction which the pod is installed - facing the fill plug toward the front leaves all three airflow channels on each side unplugged for an open direct to lung draw; and turning the pod with the fill port facing the back plugs 2.5 of each of the channels on both sides, leaving only half one one exposed for a tight mtl draw. the kit includes a pnp-vm1 dl 0.3ω mesh coil rated for 32-40w recommended for use with freebase nicotine e-liquids under 10mg and a pnp-r1 half-dl 0.8ω dual coil rated for 12-18w and recommended for use with nicotine salt e-juices under 35mg.


the vinci's gene.ai chipset supports button firing and automatic draw activation, and has a 2 week puff curve that tracks use for the last 14 days. device settings can be easily adjusted using the +/- buttons mounted below a 0.96" tft color screen, and variable wattage is supported for 5 - 40w for atomizers in the range of 0.1 - 3.0ω. the micro usb charging port is bottom mounted and supports 5v/1a quick charge under 90min.
